#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Administration Handbook"
msgstr "Administratzeko eskuliburua"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Sarrera"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is a rich educational software suite which contains a wide range "
"of activities."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; software hezitzaile suite aberats bat da, jarduera-aukera zabala "
"duena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It offers various activities aimed at covering a variety of fields. The "
"topics include reading and typing, arithmetics, geography, sciences, and "
"other topics. It is meant to be used both at home and at school."
msgstr ""
"Askotariko eremuak jorratzeko hainbat jarduera eskaintzen ditu. Gaien artean "
"daude irakurketa eta teklatu bidez idaztea, aritmetika, geografia, zientzia, "
"eta beste gai batzuk. Etxean zein eskolan erabiltzeko pentsatua dago."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The purpose of &gcompris; is to provide playful activities but always "
"educational."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris;en xedea, jarduera jostagarriak baina aldi berean hezigarriak "
"eskaintzea da."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is part of &kde; project and is placed under the <ulink url="
"\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html\">AGPLv3 license</ulink>. All "
"the code, except the engine for analog electricity activity is under <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html\">GPLv3 license</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; &kde; proiektuaren zati da eta <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/"
"licenses/agpl-3.0.html\">AGPLv3 lizentzia</ulink>pean dago. Kode guztia, "
"elektrizitate analogiko jardueraren motorra izan ezik, <ulink url=\"https://"
"www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html\">GPLv3 lizentzia</ulink>ren babespean dago."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is available on the following operating systems: &GNU;/&Linux;, "
"&BSD;, &macOS;, &Windows;, Android. It requires a 3D card with support of "
"<emphasis>OpenGL 2.1</emphasis> or higher. 32 bits color depth is mandatory."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; ondoko sistema eragileetarako eskuragarri dago: &GNU;/&Linux;, "
"&BSD; &macOS;, &Windows;, Android. <emphasis>OpenGL 2.1</emphasis> edo "
"berriagoaren euskarria duen 3D txartel bat behar du. 32 biteko kolore-"
"sakonera nahitaezkoa da."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "Instalazioa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The software is delivered under several forms. Follow the process according "
"to your case."
msgstr ""
"Softwarea hainbat eratan banatzen da. Jarraitu zure kasuaren araberako "
"prozesua."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&GNU;/&Linux;: use the packages delivered by your &GNU;/&Linux; "
"distribution. If &gcompris; is not packaged in your &Linux; distribution, "
"please contact them to ask for the inclusion of &gcompris;."
msgstr ""
"&GNU;/&Linux;: erabili zure &GNU;/&Linux; banaketak emandako paketeak. "
"Erabiltzen duzun &GNU;/&Linux; banaketan &gcompris; paketaturik ez badago, "
"mesedez, jar zaitez haiekin harremanean eta &gcompris; gehitu dezatela eska "
"iezaiezu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&Windows;: delivered under a classic installer for &Windows; or via the "
"Microsoft Store."
msgstr ""
"&Windows; : &Windows;erako instalatzaile klasiko gisa edo Microsoft "
"Saltokiaren bidez banatzen da."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "&macOS;: delivered under a classic installer."
msgstr "&macOS;: instalatzaile klasiko gisa banatzen da."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Android: distributed by the F-Droid store or Google Play Store. APK file is "
"also available."
msgstr ""
"Android: F-Droid biltegiaren bidez edo Google Play saltokiaren bidez "
"banatzen da. APK fitxategia ere eskuragarri dago."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "The User Interface"
msgstr "Erabiltzailearen interfazea"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The interface is designed for easy use by small children. &gcompris; is "
"controlled with a mouse. Keyboard navigation is also available on most of "
"the activities."
msgstr ""
"Interfazea haur txikiek erraz erabil dezaten diseinatuta dago. &gcompris; "
"sagu bidez kontrolatzen da. Jarduera gehienetan teklatuaren bidez ere "
"nabigatu daiteke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main window"
msgstr "Leiho nagusia"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start the program, &gcompris; shows a graphical interface which "
"presents the list of activities with a control bar at the bottom."
msgstr ""
"Programa abiatzen duzunean, &gcompris;-k jardueren zerrenda aurkezten duen "
"interfaze grafiko bat erakusten du, behean, aginte-barra bat duena."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here’s a screenshot of &gcompris; main window"
msgstr "Hona hemen &gcompris; leiho nagusiaren pantaila-argazki bat"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "&gcompris; Main Window"
msgstr "&gcompris; Leiho nagusia"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each icon represents an activity. Around each one, you can find small icons "
"which give additional information about the activity. A simple click on the "
"icon will lead you to an activity or a menu of activities. There are 8 "
"sections (categories) of activities, which are placed on the top or on the "
"left (only if your orientation is portrait). For example, there is section "
"“Board Games”, which includes board games, like Chess, Tic-Tac-Toe or Align "
"Four."
msgstr ""
"Ikono bakoitzak jarduera bat ordezkatzen du. Haietako bakoitzaren inguruan "
"jarduerari buruzko informazio osagarria eskaintzen duten ikono txikiak "
"aurkituko dituzu. Ikono bati klik soil bat egiteak jarduera batera edo "
"jarduera baten menu batera eramango zaitu. 8 jarduera atal (kategoria) "
"daude, goian edo ezkerrean (soilik zure orientazioa erretratua denean) "
"kokatuak. Adibidez, “Taula-jokoak” atala dago, Xakea, Hiruko artzain jokoa "
"edo Lauko artzain jokoa gisako taula-jokoak biltzen dituena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some categories have subcategories to better filter the activities. For math "
"activities, we have three subcategories: numeration, arithmetic and measures."
msgstr ""
"Kategoria batzuek azpikategoriak dituzte jarduerak hobe iragazte aldera. "
"Matematika jardueratan hiru azpikategoria ditugu: zenbatzea, aritmetika eta "
"neurriak."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "The stars indicate the age group for which each game is designed:"
msgstr ""
"Izarrek joko bakoitza zein adin talderako diseinatu den adierazten dute:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "1, 2 or 3 yellow stars — for 2 to 6 years old."
msgstr "1, 2 edo 3 izar hori — 2tik 6 urtera bitartean."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "1, 2 or 3 red stars — greater than 6 years old."
msgstr "1, 2 edo 3 izar gorri — 6 urtetik gorakoak."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the screen there is a control bar for &gcompris;. The "
"possible icons are (the icons are only displayed if they are available in "
"the activity):"
msgstr ""
"Pantailaren beheko aldean &gcompris;en aginte-barra bat dago. Izan ditzakeen "
"ikonoen artean daude (jarduerak onartzen dituenak soilik agertuko dira):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Home — Leaves the current activity, returns to the previous menu."
msgstr "Etxea — Uneko jarduera utzi eta aurreko menura itzultzen da."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"“OK” — Validate, confirm your answer. Some activities do not detect "
"automatically whether or not the child has completed the task. In this case, "
"you have to click on this icon. You can also use the &Enter; key on your "
"keyboard."
msgstr ""
"“Ados” — Zure erantzuna baieztatu, berretsi. Jarduera batzuek ez dute "
"automatikoki antzematen haurrak jarduera osatu duen. Kasu horretan, ikono "
"honi klik egin behar diozu. Zure teklatuko &Enter; tekla ere erabil dezakezu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Light — Display a hint for the activity. We can help the children on some "
"activities to guide them to find the answers."
msgstr ""
"Argia — Jarduerari buruzko pista bat erakutsi. Jarduera batzuetan haurrari "
"erantzuna aurkitzen lagundu diezaiokegu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Arrows — The present level is displayed. Click on one of the arrows to "
"select another level. Generally, the activities offer several levels whose "
"numbers depend on the activity. In &gcompris;, it is possible to go to the "
"next level without having completed the current level."
msgstr ""
"Geziak — Uneko maila azaltzen da. Egin klik gezietako batean beste maila bat "
"hautatzeko. Orokorrean, jarduerek hainbat maila eskaintzen dituzte, kopurua "
"jardueraren araberakoa da. &gcompris;en, uneko maila osatu gabe hurrengo "
"mailara igaro daiteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lips — Ask &gcompris; to repeat the question."
msgstr "Ezpainak — &gcompris;i galdera errepikatzeko eskatu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Question mark — Display the help dialog box. Sometimes, an activity can be "
"too complex to be described easily in the description area. In this case, "
"this function gives access to additional information."
msgstr ""
"Galdera ikurra — Laguntza elkarrizketa-koadroa erakutsi. Batzuetan, jarduera "
"bat konplexuegia izan daiteke azalpen eremuan modu errazean azaltzeko. Kasu "
"hauetan, funtzio honek informazio osagarria ematen du."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tool box — Configuration menu. The configuration is saved in the user "
"repository (folder) under the name <filename>.config/gcompris/gcompris-qt."
"conf</filename>. This is a text file which can be edited manually."
msgstr ""
"Tresna-kutxa — Konfiguratzeko menua. Konfigurazioa erabiltzailearen "
"gordetegian (karpeta) <filename>.config/gcompris/gcompris-qt.conf</filename> "
"izenarekin gordetzen da. Eskuz edita daitekeen testu-fitxategi bat da."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"List item — Display the activity settings menu. There are two possible tabs "
"here. First one, “Dataset”, allows to choose the levels of the activities "
"depending on several objectives and the second one, “Options”, allows to "
"update the configuration of the activity if available."
msgstr ""
"Zerrendako elementua — Jarduera-ezarpenen menua erakutsi. Hemen bi fitxa-"
"aukera daude. Lehenengoak, “Datu-multzoa”, jardueren mailak zenbait "
"helbururen arabera aukeratzen uzten du, eta bigarrenak, “Aukerak”, "
"erabilgarri badago, jardueraren konfigurazioa eguneratzen uzten du."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Capital “G” — Information box on &gcompris;, presents the main contributors "
"and the version of the software."
msgstr ""
"“G” larria — &gcompris;en gaineko informazio laukia, kolaboratzaile nagusiak "
"eta softwarearen bertsioa aurkezten ditu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Power — Quit &gcompris;. You can also use the shortcut on your keyboard "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Itzaltzea — &gcompris;etik irtetea. Zure teklatuko <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ktrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> lasterbidea ere erabil dezakezu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kiosk Mode"
msgstr "Kiosko Modua"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you use &gcompris; with small children or on a self-service kiosk, you "
"can disable a certain number of options:"
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; haur txikiekin edo autozerbitzuko kiosko batean erabiltzen "
"duzunean, aukera batzuk desgaitu ditzakezu:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris --enable-kioskmode</command></userinput>: "
"disable the <guiicon>Quit</guiicon> and <guiicon>Configuration</guiicon> "
"buttons."
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris --enable-kioskmode</command></userinput>: "
"<guiicon>Irten</guiicon> eta <guiicon>Konfiguratzea</guiicon> botoiak "
"ezgaitu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris --disable-kioskmode</command></userinput>: "
"enable the <guiicon>Quit</guiicon> and <guiicon>Configuration</guiicon> "
"buttons."
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris --disable-kioskmode</command></userinput>: "
"<guiicon>Irten</guiicon> eta <guiicon>Konfiguratzea</guiicon> botoiak gaitu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris -f</command></userinput>: run &gcompris; in "
"fullscreen mode"
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris -f</command></userinput>: &gcompris; pantaila "
"osoko moduan exekutatu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris -C</command></userinput>: disable the cursor "
"(touch screen mode)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris -C</command></userinput>: kurtsorea ezgaitu "
"(ukimen-pantaila modua)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "These options can of course be combined."
msgstr "Aukera horiek konbinatu daitezke, noski."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard Shortcuts"
msgstr "Teklatuko lasterbideak"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut"
msgstr "Lasterbidea"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Action"
msgstr "Ekintza"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Esc; or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>"
msgstr ""
"&Esc; edo <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ktrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit the current activity or dialog then return to the main menu."
msgstr ""
"Uneko jarduera edo elkarrizketa-koadroa uztea, eta, ondoren, menunagusira "
"itzultzea."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit &gcompris; without further notice."
msgstr "&gcompris;etik ezer esan gabe irtetea."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle fullscreen mode."
msgstr "Pantaila-osoko modua txandakatzea."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle sound mute."
msgstr "Soinua isilaraztea txandakatzea."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display or hide the control bar."
msgstr "Aginte-barra erakustea edo ezkutatzea."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Notes on Internationalization"
msgstr "Nazioartekotze oharrak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is internationalized and is available in more than 35 languages. "
"If you want to check if your language is available, you can start &gcompris; "
"and select your language in the option of configuration."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; nazioartekotua dago eta 35 hizkuntza baino gehiagotan erabil "
"daiteke. Zure hizkuntzan erabilgarri dagoen egiaztatzeko, &gcompris; abiatu "
"eta konfiguratzeko aukeran zure hizkuntza hauta dezakezu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Be careful, some languages need specific fonts to be displayed correctly."
msgstr ""
"Kontuz ibili, hizkuntza batzuek ondo azaltzeko letra-tipo zehatzak behar "
"dituzte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your language is not supported, you can contribute to the software and "
"add the translation of your language. If you are interested, you can contact "
"the <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams\">translation team</ulink> of "
"the &kde; project for your language. You can check the level of translation "
"for your language on the <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/\">&kde; "
"translation web site</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Zure hizkuntza onartutakoen artean ez badago, softwareari laguntzeko haren "
"itzulpena gehi dezakezu. Interesa baduzu, &kde; proiektuaren zure "
"hizkuntzarako <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams\">itzulpen taldea</"
"ulink>rekin harremanetan jar zaitezke. Zure hizkuntzarako itzulpen-maila "
"egiazta dezakezu <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/\">&kde; itzulpenaren "
"webgunean</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Language learning"
msgstr "Hizkuntzak ikastea"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use &gcompris; in a foreign language that you are learning. Select a "
"foreign language in the configuration menu. Do not forget to download the "
"optional audio modules for this language."
msgstr ""
"Ikasten ari zaren atzerriko hizkuntza batean &gcompris; erabil dezakezu. "
"Hautatu atzerriko hizkuntza bat konfigurazio-menuan. Ez ahaztu hizkuntza "
"honetarako audio-moduluak zama-jaistea."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customizing activities"
msgstr "Jarduerak norbere erara egokitzea"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can customize some activities using the configuration button in them. "
"For example, you can set the locale in some text activities (like "
"wordsgame), or make it show real car images instead of filled rectangles "
"(traffic)."
msgstr ""
"Jarduera batzuk zuk nahi duzun eran egokitu ditzakezu, haietan dagoen "
"konfiguratzeko botoia erabiliz. Esaterako, testu-jarduera batzuetan "
"(wordsgame, adibidez) tokiko ezarpenak ezar ditzakezu, edo betegarria duten "
"laukizuzenen ordez auto irudi errealak erakuts ditzan aukeratu (traffic)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For multiple activities, you can choose several datasets in the "
"configuration. Each one has a specific objective which is described."
msgstr ""
"Hainbat jardueratarako, konfiguratzean, hainbat datu-multzo hauta ditzakezu. "
"Bakoitzak deskribatzen den helburu jakin bat du."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Dataset of activity “Count the items”</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>“Zenbatu elementuak” jardueraren datu-multzoa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Dataset of activity “Count the items”</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>“Zenbatu elementuak”  jardueraren datu-multzoa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can choose the options for this activity."
msgstr "Jarduera honetarako aukerak hauta ditzakezu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Select mode of activity “Count the items”</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>“Zenbatu elementuak” jardueraren modua hautatu</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Select mode of activity “Count the items”</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Hautatu “Zenbatu elementuak”  jardueraren modua</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Console Parameters"
msgstr "Kontsolako parametroak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Running &gcompris; from a command console with the “--help” option will "
"display all the parameters it accepts:"
msgstr ""
"Komando-kontsola batean &gcompris; “--help”  aukerarekin exekutatzean "
"onartzen dituen parametro guztiak azalduko ditu:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "-f, --fullscreen"
msgstr "-f, --fullscreen"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; in fullscreen mode."
msgstr "Exekutatu &gcompris; pantaila-beteko moduan."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid "-w, --window"
msgstr "-w, --window"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; in window mode."
msgstr "Exekutatu &gcompris; leiho-moduan."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "-s, --sound"
msgstr "-s, --soinua"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; with sound enabled."
msgstr "Exekutatu &gcompris; soinua gaituta."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "-m, --mute"
msgstr "-m, --mute"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; without sound."
msgstr "Exekutatu &gcompris; soinurik gabe."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "-c, --cursor"
msgstr "-c, --cursor"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; with the default system cursor."
msgstr "Exekutatu &gcompris; sistemaren kurtsore lehenetsiarekin."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "-C, --nocursor"
msgstr "-C, --nocursor"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; without cursor (touch screen mode)."
msgstr "Exekutatu &gcompris; kurtsorerik gabe (ukimen-pantaila modua)."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v, --version"
msgstr "-v, --version"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print the version of &gcompris;."
msgstr "Inprimatu &gcompris;en bertsioa."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "-l, --list-activities"
msgstr "-l, --list-activities"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Outputs all the available activities on the standard output."
msgstr "Jarduera erabilgarri guztiak irteera estandarrean jartzen ditu."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid "--launch activity"
msgstr "--launch jarduera"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify the activity when starting &gcompris;."
msgstr "Zehaztu &gcompris; abiatzean hasiko den jarduera."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "--start-level level"
msgstr "--start-level maila"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify the level on which to start the activity specified by “--launch” "
"option when starting &gcompris;. Ignored if no “--launch” option, or if "
"level specified is invalid."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; “--launch” aukerarekin abiaraztean adierazitako jarduera zein "
"mailatan hasi behar den zehazten du. Ezikusi egiten zaio “--launch” "
"aukera»rik ez badago, edo zehaztutako maila baliogabea bada."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid "--difficulty {value|min-max}"
msgstr "--difficulty {balioa|min-max}"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the session, force &gcompris; activities difficulty to be either at "
"value or between min and max values. The values must be between 1 and 6, and "
"if the format is min-max, the min value must be lower than the max value. If "
"it is not the case &gcompris; will not start."
msgstr ""
"Saiorako, &gcompris; jardueren zailtasuna balioan edo min eta max balioen "
"artean egotea behartu. Balioek 1 eta 6 artean egon behar dute, eta formatua "
"min-max bada, min balioak max balioa baino txikiagoa izan behar du. Hala ez "
"bada  &gcompris;  ez da abiatuko."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "--export-activities-as-sql"
msgstr "--export-activities-as-sql"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export activities as SQL."
msgstr "Esportatu jarduerak SQL gisa."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "--enable-kioskmode"
msgstr "--enable-kioskmode"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable the kiosk mode (hides Quit and Configuration buttons)."
msgstr ""
"Gaitu «kiosk» modua («Irten» eta «Konfiguratzea» botoiak ezkutatzen ditu)."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "--disable-kioskmode"
msgstr "--disable-kioskmode"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disable the kiosk mode (default)."
msgstr "Desgaitu «kiosk» modua (lehenetsia)."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "--show-home-button"
msgstr "--show-home-button"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show the Home button in the bar (default)."
msgstr "Barran Etxea botoia erakutsi (lehenetsia)."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid "--hide-home-button"
msgstr "--hide-home-button"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide the Home button in the bar."
msgstr "Barran Etxea botoia ezkutatu."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "--renderer={renderer}"
msgstr "--renderer={errendatzailea}"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify which graphical renderer to use. On all platforms, “opengl” and "
"software are available. On Windows, you can use “direct3d11” or "
"“direct3d12” (if it was compiled with Qt ≥ 6.6). On &macOS;, you can use "
"“metal”."
msgstr ""
"Erabili beharreko errendatzaile grafikoa zehaztu. Plataforma guztietan "
"“opengl” eta software erabilgarri daude. Windows-en, “direct3d11” edo "
"“direct3d12” (Qt >= 6.6rekin konpilatu bazen) erabil ditzakezu. &macOS;en "
"“metal” erabil dezakezu."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "--software-renderer"
msgstr "--software-renderer"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use software renderer instead of OpenGL (should work with any graphical "
"card). Deprecated, use “--renderer=software” instead."
msgstr ""
"Erabili software errendatzailea openGLren ordez (txartel-grafiko guztiekin "
"ibili beharko litzateke). Zaharkitua, horren ordez “--renderer=software” "
"erabili."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "--opengl-renderer"
msgstr "--opengl-renderer"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use OpenGL renderer instead of software (faster and more graphical effects "
"but can crash with some graphical cards). Deprecated, use “--"
"renderer=opengl” instead."
msgstr ""
"Erabili openGL errendatzailea softwarearen ordez (azkarragoa da eta efektu "
"grafiko gehiago ditu baina txartel-grafiko batzuekin kraskatzea eragin "
"lezake). Zaharkitua, horren ordez “--renderer=opengl” erabili."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "--locale=locale"
msgstr "--locale=locale"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; with the specified locale."
msgstr "Exekutatu &gcompris; zehaztutako tokiko konfigurazioarekin."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Windows; Example"
msgstr "&Windows; Adibidea"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add these switches in the desktop icon properties. Here is an "
"example that runs &gcompris; in kiosk mode in full screen, without "
"Configuration button and cursor:"
msgstr ""
"Mahaigaineko ikonoaren propietateetan parametro hauek gehitu ditzakezu. "
"Hemen dago &gcompris; «kiosko» moduan pantaila-betean, konfiguratzeko "
"botoirik gabe eta kurtsorerik gabe exekutatzen duen adibide bat:"

#. Tag: command
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\"C:\\Program Files\\GCompris-Qt\\bin\\GCompris.exe\" --enable-kioskmode -f -"
"C"
msgstr ""
"\"C:\\Program Files\\GCompris-Qt\\bin\\GCompris.exe\" --enable-kioskmode -f -"
"C"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "&GNU;/&Linux; Example"
msgstr "&GNU;/&Linux; Adibidea"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create an application launcher and configure the command line parameters. "
"Here is an example that runs &gcompris; in kiosk mode in fullscreen, without "
"Configuration button and cursor:"
msgstr ""
"Aplikazio abiarazle bat sortu eta komando-lerroko parametroak konfiguratu. "
"Hemen dago &gcompris; kiosko moduan pantaila-betean, konfiguratzeko botoirik "
"eta kurtsorerik gabe exekutatzen duen adibide bat:"

#. Tag: command
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "gcompris-qt --enable-kioskmode -f -C"
msgstr "gcompris-qt --enable-kioskmode -f -C"

